'From Squeak2.9alpha of 13 June 2000 [latest update: #2976] on 10 November 2000 at 5:51:20 pm'!"Change Set:		ScorePlayer-fadeDate:			10 November 2000Author:			Michael RuegerImplements adjustVolumeTo:overMSecs: for ScorePlayer."!!ScorePlayer methodsFor: 'volume' stamp: 'mir 11/10/2000 08:39'!adjustVolumeTo: vol overMSecs: mSecs	| normalizedVolume incr block |	normalizedVolume _ (vol asFloat min: 1.0) max: 0.0.	incr _ (self overallVolume - normalizedVolume) / mSecs * 50.0.	block _ normalizedVolume > 0.0		ifTrue: [			[[(normalizedVolume - self overallVolume) abs > 0.01] whileTrue: [self overallVolume: self overallVolume - incr. (Delay forMilliseconds: 50) wait]]]		ifFalse: [			[[self overallVolume > 0.0] whileTrue: [self overallVolume: self overallVolume - incr. (Delay forMilliseconds: 50) wait]. self pause]].	block fixTemps; fork! !